"anchoredbilling";s:67:"Use the start of the subscription interval as a fixed billing date.";s:20:"anchoredbilling_help";s:224:"E.g. For a monthly subscription, billing will be done every 1st of the month. If a user subscribes in the middle of the month, they will be charged a prorated amount covering from the registration day to the end of the month";s:11:"trialperiod";s:12:"Trial Period";s:16:"trialperiod_help";s:341:"E.g. the first interval is free. If the subscription is created on the 24th April, a month is free and billing starts on the 24th May.<br/>
